sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  Note over API,DB: one service method, shared by POST /telemetry (status fault)<br/>and PATCH /vehicles/{id}/status
  API->>DB: SELECT vehicle FOR UPDATE (row lock serializes concurrent faults)
  API->>DB: set vehicle status = fault
  API->>DB: cancel the active mission
  API->>DB: open a maintenance record
  Note over DB: partial unique indexes make a duplicate active mission<br/>or duplicate open maintenance record impossible
  API->>DB: COMMIT
